{"serial": "63021", "department_serial": 59, "code": "SS4019", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Communications System Design I", "ch": "通訊系統設計 I"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Ying-Tsen Lin"], "ch": ["林映岑"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 1, "session": ["5", "6"]}, "loc": {"building": "S4", "room": "807"}}, {"time": {"week": 3, "session": ["Z"]}, "loc": {"building": "S4", "room": "807"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 20, "department": {"ch": "太空科學與工程學系", "en": "Department of Space Science and Engineering"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "英語", "en": "English"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 0, "selected": 20, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "修課的學生於學期末能夠針對有限的條件設計出一套基礎的通訊系統，並能指出一個通訊系統的利弊。", "en": "At the end of the course, the student should be able to design a basic communication system for ground or space communication. Upon studying a given communication system design, he or she is able to point out pros and cons about the design."}, "outline": {"ch": "此門課將介紹無線電通訊理論，並特別針對數位系統作介紹。第二部分則會利用此門課程所學，探討無線電通訊的應用。\n此門課首先概括地從其原理到應用，介紹無線電通訊系統和技術。鏈路預算的每一個環節，從無線電傳播、天線、噪音、無線電發送與接收器，也會逐步說明。通訊技術和寬頻技術的應用，會藉由地面和衛星通訊的例子得到闡述。", "en": "This course covers the principles of radio communication systems with emphasis on digital radio communication techniques. The second course in the sequence will cover applications of the principles developed in SS4019.\nThe course begins with a review of radio communication systems and techniques, including some basic communication system theory and its applications to linear systems. The factors that lead to the development of link budgets will be covered in detail - radio wave propagation, antennas, noise temperature, and radio transmitters and receivers. A review of digital radio communications techniques will follow, covering source coding and coding for error control, modulation methods, and bit error rates. Spread spectrum system will be covered with emphasis on GPS. Applications of these techniques will be illustrated with examples from broadcast, satellite, and terrestrial radio systems."}, "textbook": {"ch": "Simon Haykin, Michael Moher, Modern Wireless Communications, John Wiley, 2003, ISBN 10 0130224723\nB. P. Lathi, Z. Ding, Modern Digital and Analog Communication Systems 4th, Oxford, 2009, ISBN-13: 978-0195331455", "en": "Simon Haykin, Michael Moher, Modern Wireless Communications, John Wiley, 2003, ISBN 10 0130224723\nB. P. Lathi, Z. Ding, Modern Digital and Analog Communication Systems 4th, Oxford, 2009, ISBN-13: 978-0195331455"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "30", "en": "30"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授", "en": ["Lecture"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "作業: 30％\n實驗: 30％\n期中考: 20％\n期末考: 20％", "en": "Homework: 30％\nLab: 30％\nMid-term: 20％\nFinal exam: 20％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "星期三15:00", "en": "15:00 on Wednesdays"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "雷達與電磁波觀測\n\n\n、\n\n\n太空酬載\n\n\n、\n\n\n衛星遙測", "en": "雷達與電磁波觀測\n\n\n、\n\n\n太空酬載\n\n\n、\n\n\n衛星遙測"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "太空科學知識的建立", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}, {"competencies": "日地系統觀測技術的培養", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}, {"competencies": "整合創新與獨立思考", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "資料分析能力的養成", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "數值模式的應用", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Buildup of Space science knowledge", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Report(printed on paper)"]}, {"competencies": "Cultivation of Solar-Terrestrial observation technology", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Assignments", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Repo